1.Definition
    Create a star system on a black background
    Do so using randomness for the star size and position
    Use a for loop to generate a large amount of stars
    
2.Design
    Start > Set background to black
    Has drawn 100 stars? no > loop, yes > end
    Loop > generate random x and y coordinates >
    generate random star size > draw star
    
    PSEUDOCODE:
    START
    
    Set Background color to BLACK
    
    Repeat 100 times
    
        Generate random star position
        Generate random star size
        Draw the star
    
    End

